					<dt><a name="signup">How do I sign up?</a></dt>
					<dd>
						<font style="font-weight:normal">To sign up you must fill all the fields.
						<ul>
				
						<li><strong>Waukee Student ID</strong> - Your student username (Lastname + student id number). This is to ensure that you are a student of the Waukee community public school district.</li>
						<li><strong>First Name</strong> - Your full first name</li>
						<li><strong>Last Name</strong> - your last name.</li>
						<li><strong>E-mail Address</strong> - your e-mail address.</li>
						
						</ul>
						You will also need to have a twitter account prior to logging into Skloop. If you do not have a twtter account you can create <a href=/"http://twitter.com/signup"/>one</a>. Its easy and free to sign up! </font><br><a href="#top">>> Back to top</a>
					</dd>
