					<font style="font-weight:normal">
					Though we don't want you to stop using Skloop, we won't force you to stay.  In order to stop receiving texts, follow these steps:
					<ul><h4><em>From Web</em></h4>
						<li>Under your "Following" link (on your Profile page), find Skloop and go to its Profile page.</li>
                                                <li> Change Device Updates to "Off".</li>
                                                <li>Alternatively, to stop any text from Twitter to your phone, you can remove your phone as a device under Settings > Devices.</li>
                                                 <h4> <em>From Phone</em> </h4>
						<li>To stop texts from skloop to your phone, text <b>OFF Skloop</b>.</li>
						<li>To stop any text from Twitter to your phone, text <b>STOP</b> to <b>40404</b>.</li>
